### Get Deal Values by Lead
GET {{BASE_URL}}/statistics/deal-values-by-lead
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}

# Returns the total deal value for each deal lead.
# If a deal does not have a deal lead, the deal creator is used as the lead.

